      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior boasts its original factory finish with a deep, mirror-like gloss, free of any stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and it retains a fresh interior scent. Mechanically, the car is perfect, featuring a complete service history with every scheduled maintenance item addressed ahead of time. It sits on a set of fresh tires and has recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure everything from the electronics to the drivetrain performs flawlessly. This is a collector-grade example for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
