      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the high-revving S54 inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously overhauled for optimal valve timing. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement, paired with a precision 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. Finished in original factory paint with a pristine interior, the vehicle exhibits zero deferred maintenance. Suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the tactile feedback and balanced turn-in characteristic of a true driver's car. Comprehensive service logs and a clean DME report are available for inspection.",
